                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18420509-1586-offence-1 t18420509-cd-142"></join>6th of May</rs>, 1 pepper-castor, value 15<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; and 6 spoons, value 25<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18420509-name-858" type="victimName">
